    "summary": "I believe in Sustainable Performance Management: steering your organization towards long term value creation for all stakeholders. More specifically, it is about the Finance team in these organizations and their role to enable, support and accelerate this transformation. And it is about making it happen and realizing true impact.  My name is Marieke van der Horst, former Finance Director and experienced program manager, and it is my passion to help Financials to develop (more) sustainable businesses. How to make steps and ultimately integrate an holistic, multi-capital and long term perspective into our day-to-day business?  \n\nBy combining broad experience in Finance (business control, reporting, data & analytics) and consulting (business strategy and change programs) and my intrinsic motivation to have sustainable impact, I can help to: \n- Increase transparency on Impact, Risks & Opportunities\n- Develop CSRD/ESG compliant reporting (incl. data and ICT solution)\n- Connect you with the specialists you need along the way\n- Make roadmap to implement your impactful business strategy (integral approach)\n- Develop a Finance change program to support and accelerate this transformation\n- Manage program/projects\n- Facilitate meetings/workshops and the overall change process\n\nPlease feel free to reach out to me! \nYou can also find me on www.Tosca.nl as I recently joined this fantastic team as Associate Partner",
